name: Five sutras of Our Lady of Dreams

metadata.name: First Sutra: About our fate
metadata.description:
In the end, we are the outsiders, the ones who don't fit in, the ones who question, the ones who discomfort, the ones who observe, the non-conformists, and the ones who break, propose and create.  
We are used to chaos because we are formed in it 
there is no fear …there is no fear because we know the terror, the anguish… We face it and confront it.
